TopicTitle: V21 is here! -- Lets Get Building (Music)

Articles.Content:
I have been long awaiting this release. Stability in flight is wonderful. But who really clicked here to see me ramble??? LOL

https://soundcloud.com/billy-winn-2/lets-get-building

This one is a lil different from the last few. But I thought I would get some heads bobbing while building. I even added some industrial sounds.

It's been a while since I made a track like this.

Let me know what you think!
Cool as always! Target Eeloo is still my favorite though!
